      <title>美联储官员古尔斯比谈“极佳”就业报告、通胀和利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比 (Austan Goolsbee) 对 9 月份美国就业报告表示赞赏。古尔斯比在接受“彭博未平仓合约”节目 Mike McKee 采访时补充说，通胀率可能低于央行 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-04/fed-s-goolsbee-on-superb-jobs-report-inflation-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 14:45:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
